The best options is always to go for items fulfilled by Amazon .

Please do your part and report these things.

snippet.textDisplay:
) I live in a city affected by the coronavirus, and it's been under lockdown since the Chinese New Year (January 25). My neighborhood is barricaded, and residents aren't allowed to go out.

One afternoon my wife developed a cough. She said her throat hurt, but her temperature was normal. An hour later, she nervously showed me the thermometer: her temperature was 37.4 Celsius (99.3 Fahrenheit).
